PrecisEnactment of the (1) APPOINTMENT OF STUDENTS WITHIN THE FEDERAL SUMMER STUDENT EMPLOYMENT PROGRAM EXCLUSION APPROVAL ORDER - which exempts identified positions in the Public Service to which students are to be appointed from the application of certain provisions of the Public Service Employment Act and Regulations made thereunder, and (2) APPOINTMENT OF STUDENTS WITHIN THE FEDERAL SUMMER STUDENT EMPLOYMENT PROGRAM REGULATIONS - which are designed to facilitate the staffing of short-term positions by students.
